formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1	Sale value of the unsold property taken as certified by the management.							
2	Estimated construction value of the project taken as certified by the engineer.							
3	Technical masurement taken as provided by the management.							
4	Actual cost taken as per books of accounts upto 31.05.2019							
5	The firm has 2 phase for project development. BU has been received for 1st phase before commencement of RERA Act and accordingly RERA registration is obtained only for 2nd phase of project. Since the accounts of both the phase are not maintained separately, the cost incurred after 01.06.2015 and upto 31.05.2018 has been considered for phase 2 while issuing above certificate as informed and declared by the management.							
6	The date mentioned at column Date of agreement of sale is date of sale deed where date of agreement of sale is not available.							
7	The Account number mentioned at point 3 above is not RERA account but regular current acocunt.							
8	The details mentioned at column Allotee name, Type of KYC, KYC ID and Mobile Numberis taken as certified by the management.
